    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my reliable ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. Everything runs smoothly, and it's ready for its next adventure with you! I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
