    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six. This specimen is mechanically sound, with the critical VANOS system recently serviced and the rear subframe reinforced with plates to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight. It retains its original suspension geometry but benefits from refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers for improved damping profiles. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with a well-loved enthusiast car, the engine's compression remains within factory spec and the throttle response from the individual throttle bodies is instantaneous. A mechanically robust platform for the purist.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. No major issues.",
      "price": 34500.0,
