      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a seamless blend of performance and reliability. This unit has been curated for the discerning driver who values mechanical integrity and a clean aesthetic. Having undergone a comprehensive professional assessment, it stands as a testament to diligent ownership. Experience a refined driving dynamic and a proven track record of dependability with this premier automotive offering.",
      "price": 34850.0,
