      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for checking out my car. Honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable ride and it's still in really solid shape! It runs like a dream and has plenty of life left in it for its next owner. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I think you\u2019ll really appreciate how well it handles on the road. It\u2019s the perfect blend of comfort and value. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
