      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and feedback. To ensure long-term chassis rigidity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings were recently replaced as preventative maintenance. The suspension features refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the original factory kinematics. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and patina consistent with enthusiast use, the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline with a linear power band and no hydraulic lifter tick.",
